'''Bilmawn''' iga yan unmuggar [[Imaziɣn|amaziɣ]] ar ittili ɣ lbɛḍ n tsgiwin ɣ [[Lmɣrib]] slawan ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]], ar itilli kraygat usggwas kudnna ikml [[Lɛid mqqurn|lɛid imqqurn]]. Ar lssan ifrxan d iɛrrimn ilmawn n tfaska d ar sis tḍwarn ɣ tmdint nɣ udwar.

==Aẓur ==
Anmuggar ad izdi d tamiṭulujit tamaziɣt taqburt

==Anmuggar==
[[Afaylu:Boujloud.jpg|vignette|Bilmawn n ayt [[Lḥawz]]]]
Ar ittadda unmuggar ɣ wass amzwaru n lɛid mqqurn, d ar gis ittili 3 wussan bɛd lɛid ɣ idwarn, d izḍar ad akk izri imalass ɣ kran tmdinin. Ɣ tfugla ad, tuggt n middn d ifrxan ar lssan ilmawn n izammarn n tfaska, ar tsbaɣn idmawn nnsn, nɣ ar lssan lmask, Ar disn ttasin iḍarn n izimr ɣ ifassn nnsn, d ar sisn slayn middn lli disn iḥtafln. Ar disn ttili lbɛḍ n twal yat trabbut n umarg. Awttas n tfugla ad tga tt ad fjjijn middn ilin d lxwaṭr nnsn.

Ɣ tfugla ad, ar ttilin ɣayd n middn nna d yakkan iqariḍn ar sisn tbrraɛn fad ad skrn inmuggarn nna ɣ tḥaḍarn tuggt n middn ku-yan d mani d yucka. Anmuggar lli akk imqqurn n Bilmawn iga s yism " ''Bilmawn Bidmawn'' " ar ittili ɣ tmdint n [[Dcayra]], ɣ [[Tamnbaḍt n Inzggan-Ayt Mllul|Inzggan-Ayt Mllul]].

